item.title: Hello world
item.description: Who I am Well, the truth is, I’m a person who doesn’t like to repeat myself too much. So I’ll leave here the link to the page where I have already written about who I am. What I am going to talk about I’m going to write about almost everything. But above all, about software development, Go and myself. I know it doesn’t sound very interesting or very original. But well, I didn’t say it’s going to be either.
